A bloody shooting spree in Umlazi s G-Section in the early hours of Saturday morning left three people dead and 12 people wounded.It is understood that a group of gunmen ran rampant at a tavern spraying automatic gunfire at patrons before making their way to a house in the same street. Inside the house on Mandla Mandlotha Street three people were murdered one of them a woman who had also been rapedPolice confronted the suspects at the house and shot and killed one of the gang members.Government officials were set to visit the house later on Saturday. TMG Digital 